<div class="tw-foot p"><div class="fn" id="TFN1"><p><strong>Notes:</strong> CI=Confidence Interval;
CV/DM/Lipids=Cardiovascular disease, diabetes mellitus, and
hyperlipidemia.</p></div></div></section><section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="T3"><h4 class="obj_head">Table 3.</h4>
<div class="caption p"><p>Exposure to novel therapeutics approved by the Food and Drug Administration
between 2005 and 2012 during pivotal efficacy trials that provided the basis for
approval, stratified by therapeutic and indication characteristics.</p></div>
<div class="tbl-box p" tabindex="0"><table class="content" frame="box" rules="all">
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left" valign="middle" rowspan="2" colspan="1">Therapeutic/Indication
Characteristic</th>
<th align="center" valign="middle" rowspan="2" colspan="1">Pivotal Trials, No.</th>
<th colspan="2" align="center" valign="middle" rowspan="1">Median Patients, No.
(IQR)</th>
